{
  "stem": "17543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It sort of make it like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know-- it's a-- it's a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] something to be proud of or something.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's terrible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's really terrible to know that to have in their homes things from people who've been killed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This is terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's later on I heard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So as later-- later on, more and more I heard of, you know, which I didn't know then.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, I had no idea what happened to my father's business, because it was expensive machinery, which he worked since he was 16, and my mother, as well, because they was very young when they met.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My mother worked as a dressmaker, and he was worked around the clock in manufacturing somewhere.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they all worked extremely hard to have what they . had been just taken away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the only thing I want to say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Jews wasn't fighting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Jews wasn't taking guns and fighting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they can't be really regarded as war-- anything to do with the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Or just didn't want to say a certain part of a country where they were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They want to declare it is theirs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So it just wasn't in the army either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I mean, how can be the Jews of these European countries-- that I know Hungary.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They was not done anything which made them-- the government of that time-- make them unsuitable to be in the country, because they wasn't doing anything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was just earning their keep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that's all they was doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He wasn't involved into anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So can't compare it to civil wars of other countries where people are fighting for some reason with guns.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1956, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was a frightening experience, because I couldn't walk on the streets.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
